New version (0.31) of geo2tag-core was released.

Key features:
  * Riak support added
  * Coordinates precision improved
  * filterSubstring request added

Full list of resolved tasks.
https://geo2tag.atlassian.net/issues/?filter=12000


Before updating please install Riak using this instruction
http://docs.basho.com/riak/latest/downloads/

Description of the riak-releated features can be found here
http://geo2tag.org/index.php/Exchange_protocol
